[{"title":"PotPlayer 免安装绿色版","url":"http://51simple.com/2017/02/04/potplayer-green-version-md/","content":"<p>PotPlayer是Windows下非常优秀的一款音视频播放器，支持大多数的文件格式。官网只有安装版，这里提供免安装的版本，<a href=\"http://pan.baidu.com/s/1kV2pqE7点\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">点此下载</a></p>\n<p>下载之后，解压出一个PotPlayer文件夹，里面有个<code>PotPlayerMini.exe</code>，选中它并右键，选择<code>发送到</code>-&gt;<code>桌面快捷方式</code>。</p>\n","categories":["软件工具"],"tags":["免安装版"]},{"title":"BaiduPCS - 百度网盘命令行工具(不限速)","url":"http://51simple.com/2017/02/04/baidupcs/","content":"<p>BaiduPCS 是一个多线程下载或上传百度网盘的命令行工具，可以在linux终端中使用。当然也支持Windows, Mac平台，关键在于<code>不限速</code>。</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<p>简单介绍一下windows下的使用方法：<br>1、下载 <a href=\"http://pan.baidu.com/s/1miFe1r6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">pcs.exe</a>，并移到到个人用户目录下（如 C:\\用户\\Simple）<br>2、按Win+r快捷键，输入cmd回车，即可打开命令窗口<br>3、执行 <code>pcs set --max_thread=3</code>设置最大下载线程数<br>4、执行 <code>pcs login --username=gang --password=&quot;password&quot;</code> ，对应自己的帐号密码进行登陆<br>5、之后就是一些操作文件的命令，详情见作者<a href=\"https://github.com/GangZhuo/BaiduPCS/blob/master/README.md#命令列表&quot;\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">github主页</a></p>\n<p>提示：把 pcs.exe 所在目录加入到系统的环境变量（Path）中会更方便，这样不管当前目录是什么，都能使用 pcs 命令。</p>\n","categories":["Tutorial"],"tags":["百度云不限速"]},{"title":"Linux去除烦人的sudo密码","url":"http://51simple.com/2017/02/04/linux-remove-sudo-password/","content":"<p>执行sudo命令需要频繁输入密码，虽说更安全，但也挺烦人的，我选择去除它。</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<p>打开终端，执行<code>sudo visudo</code>，找到这一行：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">%sudo  ALL=(ALL:ALL) ALL</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>在行首添加<code>#</code>，即注释掉此行，再往下添加一行：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">%sudo ALL=NOPASSWD:ALL</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>保存修改之后，以后执行sudo命令就畅通无阻了。</p>\n","categories":["Linux"],"tags":["sudo密码"]},{"title":"","url":"http://51simple.com/css/custom.css","content":"","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"about","url":"http://51simple.com/about/index.html","content":"","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"link","url":"http://51simple.com/link/index.html","content":"","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"search","url":"http://51simple.com/search/index.html","content":"","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"tag","url":"http://51simple.com/tag/index.html","content":"","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"category","url":"http://51simple.com/category/index.html","content":"","categories":[],"tags":[]}]